Q.1 can I store ami in s3 bucket ?
CreateStoreImageTask рд╣реЗ EC2 API
 CreateRestoreImageTask рд╡рд╛рдкрд░реВрди рдкрд░рдд AMI рдордзреНрдпреЗ Restore рдХрд░реВ рд╢рдХрддрд╛.
ami-xxxxxxxx.bin
this method is primarily used for long-term archival or when you need to move an AMI across AWS accounts or regions in a way that doesn't use the standard AMI copy feature.
AWS provides specific tools to package an entire AMI and its associated data into a single, compressed object that is stored in an S3 bucket that you own and manage.
